                        <h1>Election day set for 9 September 2013</h1>
                    
                
                
            </div>
        </div>
    
    


<div class="documentBody" id="Tekstinnhold">
    
    
    
        <div>
            

<p><strong>The Cabinet meeting today set Monday, 9 September 2013 as the date for the 2013 parliamentary (Storting) election and the Sami parliament election.<br /></strong><br />The individual municipal councils can determine whether or not their municipalities will also allow voting on Sunday, 8 September 2013.</p>
<p><br />The Ministry of Local Government and Regional Development’s media contact line: +47 22 24 25 00<br /></p>
